{"tid":2463210,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(推到完場)SpaceX Starship SN11 Test Flight (如果靜態點火成功)","createTime":"2021-03-26T13:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:14:54.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8202db4b8c3f1d1b1f83c2a8cf2140f760ab94bb","tid":2463210,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJXEq9IX1To\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJJXEq9IX1To&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=765eec1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JJXEq9IX1To</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sTA0GTgFn5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsTA0GTgFn5E&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=63d19604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sTA0GTgFn5E</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">日經常見問題︰</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&mdash; </strong>星艦係由兩個部份組成，上層的starship同下層的助推器superheavy。當整支星艦去到軌道後助推器superheavy便會分離返回地球，starship則視任務而定會否在軌道接受多次加油，還是直接飛住目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8JyvzU0CXU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC8JyvzU0CXU&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=c21abfa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8JyvzU0CXU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&mdash;</strong> 星艦系統將會係人類歷史上除土星5號外最大型的火箭，同時都係第一支完成可重用的火箭，現時的獵鷹9號及重型獵鷹只是一級推重器及有整流罩可重用，若星艦成功，其探索成本將有望進一步降低，運載成本也將比獵鷹9號更低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRyNM5ikAuMaii1rYNmaigMRAcD9AEAwGgKWD75CnzGgS?filename=Qb1p2s1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQb1p2s1.png&h=61692f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&mdash; </strong>上層的starship既測試原型機SN系列預計會去到SN20，但因為進度比預計快消息指SN12-SN14已被取消，重心放在SN15-SN20，將會有重大更新及更高的高空飛行測試。下部份的BN系列也預計將在年中開始測試，BN1原型機已接近完工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNW5QK1ejRFZm4B4GHZn9Py3WfWLFqcPZJ5RQkD2KzSBh?filename=3hUbHs6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hUbHs6.jpg&h=7d783cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&mdash; </strong>星艦不同其他火箭，是由不鏽鋼組成，其強度比碳複合材料高。但其實不鏽鋼正常唔會用係火箭到，因為過重，但elon認為不鏽鋼係低溫同高溫下表現更出色，減去因此少用左既絕緣陶瓦反而成支既重量會更低，而且不鏽鋼的平價同易造令快速生產成為可能。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>&mdash;</strong> 藍色起源的所謂可重用火箭不論體積及飛行高度都遠不及獵鷹9號，也無法進入地球軌道，因此獵鷹9號到現時還是<strong><span class=\"red\">世界上唯二</span></strong>的可重用的重型及中型運載火箭，所以大家聽少D jeff bezos吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RQe_I0Zmzuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRQe_I0Zmzuk&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=678c2379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RQe_I0Zmzuk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSoAgy1SBSvaK6SBmX6aKC3uoQb8PjbWi37CkKhux5rpw?filename=rYC1ke2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrYC1ke2.jpg&h=86a26019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmevc1eRFNg24MQTBcaGtt1Hm4v3Y9MWZf9ZN9qDVQERkL?filename=dfsApGH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfsApGH.jpg&h=9c09164c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbPAippdWe1F18f2YxrZWgkiJLRCyBbiDxe8geSsSUW3i?filename=rcAFAOn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcAFAOn.jpg&h=cd8f4f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNvZEt1jLCXsxYoHXgXer1vXgpHQzwLoyzQ1TFdhCAfYg?filename=G6OLMU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6OLMU2.jpg&h=dc9aa49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV3g9B6xLJxXy9BxHisjvXy5ot15CzuBAmwcMNPEgTSDN?filename=xYswHtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYswHtn.jpg&h=63195742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPEAQxNEfhdf42fiSh9qRWeiP3kKm1q9RFCsF2i8LL33J?filename=zpSHO8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpSHO8n.jpg&h=cf455dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNkxTZk6Fy2ArUp2iTjRatnvfTntK4UkXN53NAjQpLgAg?filename=8oAeFe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oAeFe2.jpg&h=2c4fc7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQEYVQApB9oU3jgFB8KegCgQBgXs78CAjMvqzxy24YR97?filename=Ex742tn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEx742tn.jpg&h=8c7917ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTv2cUEDdF7wai55FPKaEsG2mprjxZ9JpzwFgFHHpcbZm?filename=i0uK2tn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0uK2tn.jpg&h=3de43384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbuAEtm4JTBf1BgYEA2YHjW6Zn46Ka4THDw6qE1FQLqC8?filename=Yhd4h1H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhd4h1H.gif&h=53242eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRDPbANV7e74sPFxe8eWPuxgWxNPGvE6Xy9jCGEHcyqXU?filename=h9GUFe3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9GUFe3.gif&h=c0048bc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f223d0a5f626a72b7a26a7fe9429d8c2fb0c0c3d","tid":2463210,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"如果靜態點火成功的話，今日將有大機會進行試飛"},{"pid":"338de6b25e0399c9c17b42637a2dee4cbc25a426","tid":2463210,"uid":336590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b119f003